data.description: Your perfect oasis in Homestead awaits!. Single family home, 4 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms. Excellent Location, close to downtown Homestead, Krome ave, US1, FL turnpike, parks, great schools, major shopping centers & restaurants!.Nestled in a serene neighborhood with no HOA fees, this home exudes a tranquil ambiance. Upgraded kitchen and laundry room. Don't miss the opportunity to make this your forever home!. Storage shed (6x9).   4% seller contributions at full price. Price can be negotiated on the same amount of the seller contribution.
